metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"App"}, 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"Sumconversions", CALCULATE(SUM('blinkit_marketing_performance'[conversions])),
			"Sumspend", CALCULATE(SUM('blinkit_marketing_performance'[spend]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [Sumconversions], 0, 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Sumconversions] DESC, 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience]

		TOPN(6, __DS0ScopedPreLimitL0, 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel], 1)

	VAR __DS0ScopedLimitL1 = 
		TOPN(
			__DS0LimitBlock1LimitCount,
			__DS0ScopedPreLimitL1,
			'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience],
			1
		)

	VAR __SyncDS0SyncTable = 
		SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
			ADDCOLUMNS(
				KEEPFILTERS(__DS0ScopedLimitL1),
				"Clonedtarget_audience", 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience]
			),
			"SyncI0",
			SELECTCOLUMNS(
				KEEPFILTERS(__DS0ScopedLimitL1),
				"Clonedtarget_audience", 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience]
			),
			[Clonedtarget_audience],
			ASC
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyRegroupedToDM1ScopedLimitedL1 = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__SyncDS0SyncTable,
			__DS0Core
		)

	VAR __IsDM1Valid = 
		CALCULATE(NOT(ISEMPTY(__DS0BodyRegroupedToDM1ScopedLimitedL1)))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0ScopedLimitL0,
			ADDCOLUMNS(
				KEEPFILTERS(__DS0BodyRegroupedToDM1ScopedLimitedL1),
				"IsDM1Valid", __IsDM1Valid
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0ScopedPreLimitL0Count", __DS0ScopedPreLimitL0Count,
		"DS0ScopedLimitL0Count", 6,
		"DS0ScopedPreLimitL1Count", __DS0ScopedPreLimitL1Count,
		"DS0ScopedLimitL1Count", __DS0LimitBlock1LimitCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0ScopedLimitL1

ORDER BY
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience]

EVALUATE
	GROUPBY(
		__DS0Core,
		"MinSumspend", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Sumspend]),
		"MaxSumspend", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Sumspend]),
		"Minblinkit_marketing_performanceSumspend", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [blinkit_marketing_performanceSumspend]),
		"Maxblinkit_marketing_performanceSumspend", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [blinkit_marketing_performanceSumspend])
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel],
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"All"}, 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[target_audience])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		CALCULATETABLE(
			SUMMARIZE(
				'blinkit_marketing_performance',
				'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel],
				'blinkit_marketing_performance'[spend],
				'blinkit_marketing_performance'[conversions]
			),
			KEEPFILTERS(__DS0FilterTable)
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample = 
		SAMPLECARTESIANPOINTSBYCOVER(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'blinkit_marketing_performance'[spend],
			'blinkit_marketing_performance'[conversions]
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyOverlappingPointsSample

ORDER BY
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel],
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[spend],
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[conversions]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel],
			"Averagecrpc", CALCULATE(AVERAGE('blinkit_marketing_performance'[crpc]))
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(1002, __DS0Core, 'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'blinkit_marketing_performance'[channel]
